<LanguageData>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_CitadelEngineer.description>[PAWN_nameDef] specialized in maintaining the Citadel's defenses and infrastructure, ensuring the Pride's strongh老旧 remained secure against all threats.</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_CitadelEngineer.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_CitadelEngineer.title>城堡工程师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_CitadelEngineer.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_CitadelEngineer.titleShort>工程师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_CitadelEngineer.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Cook.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 维持城堡的饮食，为骑士和文士准备丰盛的饭菜，并为骄傲队提供的每顿饭菜都鼓舞士气。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Cook.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Cook.title>骄傲厨师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Cook.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Cook.titleShort>厨师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Cook.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Demolitions_Expert.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 专门从事爆炸物、清理瓦砾和摧毁敌方防御工事，以便骄傲队在首都荒原的行动。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Demolitions_Expert.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Demolitions_Expert.title>爆破专家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Demolitions_Expert.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Demolitions_Expert.titleShort>拆除</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Demolitions_Expert.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Field_Instructor.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 在武器操作、战术和生存方面训练新兵，塑造下一代里昂骄傲战士。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Field_Instructor.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Field_Instructor.title>现场讲师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Field_Instructor.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Field_Instructor.titleShort>讲师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Field_Instructor.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Mechanic.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 维护傲慢号的载具和动力装甲，确保每台机器都做好随时战斗的准备。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Mechanic.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Mechanic.title>骄傲机械师</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Mechanic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Mechanic.titleShort>机械</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Mechanic.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Power_Armor_Operator.description>[PAWN_nameDef] mastered the use and maintenance of power armor, leading charges against 超级变种人 and protecting Lyons' Pride interests with unmatched resilience.</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Power_Armor_Operator.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Power_Armor_Operator.title>动力装甲操作员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Power_Armor_Operator.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Power_Armor_Operator.titleShort>装甲操作员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Power_Armor_Operator.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Quartermaster.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 管理骄傲队的军械库，向骑士和文士分发武器和补给品，并确保在生存之战中不浪费任何东西。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Quartermaster.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Quartermaster.title>军需</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Quartermaster.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Quartermaster.titleShort>军需</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Quartermaster.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Recon_Specialist.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 擅长侦察敌人阵地和收集情报，经常冒险深入敌方领土以确保骄傲队的战术优势。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Recon_Specialist.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Recon_Specialist.title>侦察专家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Recon_Specialist.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Recon_Specialist.titleShort>侦察</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Recon_Specialist.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Salvage_Team_Leader.description>[PAWN_nameDef] led expeditions into 危险 废墟s, recovering valuable technology and resources for the Pride's continued survival.</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Salvage_Team_Leader.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Salvage_Team_Leader.title>打捞队长</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Salvage_Team_Leader.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Salvage_Team_Leader.titleShort>打捞者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Salvage_Team_Leader.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Scout_Leader.description>[PAWN_nameDef] led reconnaissance teams through the 废墟s of DC, mapping safe routes and identifying threats before they could strike for the Pride.</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Scout_Leader.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Scout_Leader.title>童军领袖</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Scout_Leader.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Scout_Leader.titleShort>童军领袖</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Scout_Leader.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Wasteland_Defender.description>After years of training, [PAWN_nameDef] became a full-fledged Knight, patrolling the 废墟s of DC and defending settlements from raiders and mutants. [PAWN_pronoun] earned a reputation for bravery and tactical skill among the Lyons' Pride.</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Wasteland_Defender.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Wasteland_Defender.title>荒地卫士</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Wasteland_Defender.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Wasteland_Defender.titleShort>后卫</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Knight_Wasteland_Defender.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Lyons_Pride_Veteran.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 与传奇的里昂之傲并肩作战，面对首都废土的最大威胁。 [PAWN_pronoun] 因 [PAWN_possessive] 的勇气和对骄傲队理想坚定不移的忠诚而受到尊重。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Lyons_Pride_Veteran.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Lyons_Pride_Veteran.title>里昂的骄傲老将</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Lyons_Pride_Veteran.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Lyons_Pride_Veteran.titleShort>骄傲老兵</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Lyons_Pride_Veteran.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Outcast_Hunter.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 的任务是追踪和对抗流放者，执行里昂长老的愿景并保护骄傲组织的团结。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Outcast_Hunter.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Outcast_Hunter.title>被遗弃的猎人</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Outcast_Hunter.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Outcast_Hunter.titleShort>被遗弃的猎人</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Paladin_Outcast_Hunter.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Archivist.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 奉献了 [PAWN_possessive] 一生来保存骄傲的历史，并对每一项回收的技术和知识进行编目。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Archivist.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Archivist.title>档案管理员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Archivist.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Archivist.titleShort>档案管理员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Archivist.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Communications_Officer.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 维持巡逻队和城堡之间的无线电联系，协调任务并为荒地中的骄傲队传递重要信息。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Communications_Officer.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Communications_Officer.title>传讯官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Communications_Officer.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Communications_Officer.titleShort>通讯官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Communications_Officer.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Diplomat.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 代表里昂之傲与废土定居点和敌对派系进行谈判，建立联盟并确保资源。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Diplomat.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Diplomat.title>骄傲外交官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Diplomat.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Diplomat.titleShort>外交官</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Diplomat.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Field_Researcher.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 前往荒地研究变异的动植物群，为狮群提供宝贵的科学见解和生存知识。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Field_Researcher.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Field_Researcher.title>实地研究员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Field_Researcher.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Field_Researcher.titleShort>实地研究员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Field_Researcher.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Researcher.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 专注于开发新的治疗方法和药物，利用战前知识和荒地发现来治愈骄傲队的伤员。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Researcher.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Researcher.title>医学研究员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Researcher.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Researcher.titleShort>医学研究员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Researcher.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Specialist.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 致力于拯救生命，成为一名医学专家，治疗受伤的里昂骄傲成员并研究先进的治疗技术。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Specialist.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Specialist.title>医疗专家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Specialist.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Specialist.titleShort>军医</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Medical_Specialist.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Technology_Seeker.description>作为一名抄写员，[PAWN_nameDef] 在荒原上搜寻失落的知识和战前技术，为里昂骄傲档案馆记录每一项发现。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Technology_Seeker.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Technology_Seeker.title>技术探索者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Technology_Seeker.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Technology_Seeker.titleShort>技术探索者</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Scribe_Technology_Seeker.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 早年花费 [PAWN_possessive] 帮助骄傲档案管理员保存和研究战前文件，了解历史和记录保存的重要性。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.title>档案员助理</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.titleShort>档案管理员</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Archivist_Assistant.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Bunker_Born.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 在城堡的坚固城墙内出生并长大。从很小的时候起，[PAWN_pronoun] 就了解了纪律、秩序的价值以及技术在重建文明中的重要性，这是里昂骄傲的一部分。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Bunker_Born.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Bunker_Born.title>地堡诞生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Bunker_Born.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Bunker_Born.titleShort>地堡诞生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Bunker_Born.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Canteen_Apprentice.description>虽然骄傲队回避奢侈品，但长老们承认，一顿像样的饭菜可以鼓舞士气。作为一名乡绅，[PAWN_nameDef]表现出了烹饪天赋，并经常帮助食堂工作人员。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Canteen_Apprentice.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Canteen_Apprentice.title>食堂学徒</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Canteen_Apprentice.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Canteen_Apprentice.titleShort>食堂学徒</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Canteen_Apprentice.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Field_Medic.description>被分配到医疗舱后，[PAWN_nameDef] 学​​习了基本的急救和战场分诊，为 [PAWN_objective] 准备应对荒地战斗的严酷现实，这是里昂骄傲的一部分。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Field_Medic.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Field_Medic.title>战地军医乡绅</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Field_Medic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Field_Medic.titleShort>战地医疗兵</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Field_Medic.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Junior_Medic.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 协助 Pride 医务人员进行基本急救，并学会了照顾伤员，培养了稳定的双手和富有同情心的心。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Junior_Medic.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Junior_Medic.title>初级军医</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Junior_Medic.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Junior_Medic.titleShort>初级军医</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Junior_Medic.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 通过帮助组织骄傲队食堂的膳食和用品，确保每个人都有饭吃，学会了责任感和团队合作。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.title>食堂管家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.titleShort>混乱管家</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Mess_Hall_Steward.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Messenger.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 被信任在整个城堡内传递消息和物资，了解可靠性和快速思维在骄傲行动中的重要性。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Messenger.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Messenger.title>乡绅信使</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Messenger.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Messenger.titleShort>信使</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Messenger.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.description>从很小的时候起，[PAWN_nameDef]就对傲慢号标志性的动力装甲着迷。 [PAWN_pronoun] 花费了无数时间学习维护并最终操作这些技术奇迹。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.title>动力装甲实习生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.titleShort>铠甲实习生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Power_Armor_Trainee.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scout_In_Training.description>From a young age, [PAWN_nameDef] was taught to navigate the 废墟s of DC, learning stealth, observation, and survival skills from Pride scouts.</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scout_In_Training.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scout_In_Training.title>侦察员训练中</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scout_In_Training.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scout_In_Training.titleShort>见习童子军</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scout_In_Training.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.description>[PAWN_nameDef] was chosen by a Pride Scribe for early mentorship, learning to read, write, and analyze 古老 texts and schematics.</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.title>文士的学生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.titleShort>文士的学生</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Scribes_Pupil.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.description>Fascinated by pre-war relics, [PAWN_nameDef] spent [PAWN_possessive] youth assisting Pride Scribes in restoring 古老 technology, learning the value of knowledge and patience.</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.title>技术学徒</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.titleShort>技术学徒</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Tech_Apprentice.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.description>[PAWN_nameDef] 因袭击者而成为孤儿，被里昂骄傲巡逻队救出并被赋予了新的使命。城堡里的生活很严格，但[PAWN_pronoun]在骄傲的指导下蓬勃发展。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.description>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.title>废土孤儿</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.titleShort>孤儿</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Wasteland_Orphan.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Workshop_Helper.description>小时候，[PAWN_nameDef] 经常出现在骄傲的工作室里，在资深机械师的注视下学习修理武器和盔甲。</FCP_Backstory_BoS_Lyons_Pride_Squire_Workshop_Helper.description>
